transcripts: So this is the deluxe high reach cleaning kit from bed bath and beyond the cleaning kit is a cost effective solution for homes with high ceilings and allows you to access hard to reach places with ease. This cleaning kit includes a clamp changer squeegee and microfiber scrubber a bendable duster cobweb duster broken bulb changer suction bulb changer and an eight foot telescoping pole the pole allows you to reach up to 14 feet and easily retracts for convenient storage when not in use. The deluxe high reach cleaning kit available online or at a bed bath and beyond near you.
